{"tid":837152,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[求相認]成日見人屌啲濕鳩同事,有冇人就係果啲濕鳩","createTime":"2018-09-26T07:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-04T17:44:13.000Z","uid":23197,"like":6,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"58594ddddeef7e7c9b288c3c1add0fea10ae5981","tid":837152,"uid":23197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:18:12.000Z","msg":"做濕鳩既感覺真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇同路人一齊分享下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n老細開會果陣想搵我負責某樣野，即刻擺個老屎忽樣叫個同職位，唔夠我年資耐既同事做，睇準老細淨係想有人跟單野，射得就射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同事一做錯小小野就大大聲屌鳩佢等全世界都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同事過黎搵我幫手，西鳩佢面就基本，之後再屌下佢廢，然後幫完擺個拯救者既姿態話俾全世界知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n實在太多，諗到再加"},{"pid":"c0bbe6b6ae53e9fc236771bc48ac356af4802dd4","tid":837152,"uid":23197,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:31:22.000Z","msg":"連登有冇同路人牙=.="},{"pid":"da016d55c87c6224ff38a1835f63ad1befeb43ba","tid":837152,"uid":23197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T07:51:54.000Z","msg":"渣ga=.= 唔通呢到個個都勤力小蜜蜂"},{"pid":"5d316fd0c1c4316a8341c302415f9d4a3a21d2e1","tid":837152,"uid":23197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"淨係six負評=.="},{"pid":"df872cf44dcc9a080a1175d7f9a11724b5043384","tid":837152,"uid":23197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-26T17:15:27.000Z","msg":"渣ga連登仔=.="},{"pid":"ee5f71a9f50b27ab7e99a7abad18f7f3b1cc2b3a","tid":837152,"uid":23197,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T12:44:52.000Z","msg":"30個負評但係無回覆=.="},{"pid":"b4c55b406357bab0d31c6817957de3c570ae08bf","tid":837152,"uid":192808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-04T16:32:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"678584976c144673897